          On top of my day-to-day work, I also do consulting on side. Helping
          companies and individuals to solve their problems or develop new
          solutions. <a href="/consulting">See how I can help you</a>.
        </p> -->

        <!-- <p>
          When I am not in front of my computer or a book, I try to move as much
          as possible: running or cycling in the Belgian countryside, practicing
          wa-jutsu (a non-competive martial art) or hiking in nature.
        </p> -->

        <!-- <center>◦◦◦</center>

        <p>
          This site also host my <a href="/blog">blog</a> where I write about topics
          I am interested in such as programming languages, DevOps, testing or software
          quality. Writing allows me to cristallize my thoughts.
        </p> -->
      </div>
      <div class="m-4 md:my-0">
        <Image
          src={mePic}
          alt="Charles Vandevoorde, software engineer"
          class="rounded-xl"
          format="webp"
        />
      </div>
    </MaxWidth>
  </div>

  <MaxWidth class="mt-10">
    <div class="flex flex-row items-center space-x-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl inline-block py-10">Recent posts</h2>
      <hr class="flex-1 w-full py-[1px] bg-zinc-500" />
    </div>

    <BlogList blogs={entries} />
  </MaxWidth>
</Layout>
